task.en: Get me to the Diffusers github page. Use private browsing.
task.zh: 用隐私浏览打开Diffusers的github repo页面。
task.ar: قم بتوجيه المتصفح لفتح صفحة Diffusers على GitHub باستخدام التصفح الخاص.
task.ja: プライベートブラウジングモードを使って、DiffusersのGitHubリポジトリページを開いてください。
task.ru: Используя приватный режим браузера, откройте страницу репозитория Diffusers на GitHub.

grading_command: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "GitHub - huggingface/diffusers" && osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -Eq "(Private Browsing|无痕浏览|التصفح الخاص|プライベートブラウズ|частный доступ)" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "GitHub - huggingface/diffusers" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -Eq "(Private Browsing|无痕浏览|التصفح الخاص|プライベートブラウズ|частный доступ)" && echo "True" || echo "False"
